These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, scooter, roller
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, western
1. the person watching mystery movies is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the roller is the person watching western movies##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Transport   | helicopter | scooter | roller   |
| Movie-Genre      | musical    | mystery  | western |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, ivory, fuchsia
3 different pets are kept: ferret, dog, fish
1. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the dog is the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Color      | ivory | purple     | fuchsia      |
| Pet   | dog | ferret | fish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, russian, argentine
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, lawyer, dancer
1. the russian is on the right of the lawyer##1
2. the argentine is on the left of the dancer##1
3. the indian is on the left of the lawyer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Nationality   | indian | argentine  | russian       |
| Job       | chef     | lawyer | dancer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, american, argentine
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, weightlifting, surfing
1. the american is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the polish is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Nationality    | argentine    | american     | polish |
| Sport   | surfing | baseball | weightlifting     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, march, december
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, writer, librarian
1. the writer is the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the writer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the architect##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Birthday         | march | january     | december |
| Job   | librarian        | architect | writer    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
City: paris, rome, venice
House: futuristic, palace, farmhouse
1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the futuristic house##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the palace house##1
3. the person traveling to venice is the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| City        | venice | paris      | rome  |
| House   | futuristic       | palace | farmhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, pumpkin, strawberry
City: liverpool, rome, hamburg
1. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is the person traveling to rome##1
3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Food   | strawberry      | pomegranate     | pumpkin    |
| City           | liverpool | hamburg | rome |

