1. the colonial house is the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Birthday   | august | september | december  |
