There 3 different types of food: mango, apple, pineapple
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who likes white##1
2. the person eating pineapple is on the far right##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who likes azure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Color      | ivory   | white    | azure    |
| Food   | apple | mango | pineapple |

