The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, surfing
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
2. the person who likes blue is in the middle##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Color   | yellow     | blue   | mauve     |
| Sport    | surfing | parkour | lacrosse |

