.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-14::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, disaster, western
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, italian, japanese
1. the japanese is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Movie-Genre   | animation    | western | disaster |
| Nationality   | japanese | thai     | italian        |

