.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, ship, snowmobile
3 different games are played: monopoly, poker, snooker
1. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Transport      | train  | snowmobile | ship  |
| Game   | poker | snooker   | monopoly |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-16::.
City: marseilles, colone, hamburg
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, dubstep, classical
1. the fan of dubstep is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| City   | colone | marseilles | hamburg    |
| Music-Genre        | reggae    | classical | dubstep |

