.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-17::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, cola
3 different pets are kept: turtle, dog, fish
1. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the turtle is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Beverage           | iced-tea | cola | coffee |
| Pet   | fish  | turtle      | dog |

