.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, almond-milk
3 different pets are kept: lizard, rabbit, frog
1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the person drinking 7up is the owner of the frog##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk | almond-milk   | 7up        |
| Pet   | rabbit    | lizard | frog |

