1. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who likes fuchsia##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Pet         | frog | chinchilla | bird |
| Color   | apricot | fuchsia     | pink  |

