.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, may, march
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, woodworking, camping
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Birthday    | march | june       | may  |
| Hobby   | camping  | woodworking | collecting |

 